# Track strategy param artifacts as config-as-code: small JSON files that are
# baked into the runner image (param_store resolves the local file first, so no
# blob/env/network is needed). Re-include only this subtree; everything else
# under data/ (parquet feeds, scratch json) stays ignored.
!data/strategy_params
!data/strategy_params/**

